mapping
This package contains the mapping layer.
mapping.errors  
mapping.exceptions
This package contains exceptions of the mapping layer.
mapping.get
This package contains the functionality to read values retrieved from FHEM via 'jsonlist2' command or websocket message and map it to models.
mapping.get.functionMapper
This package provides functionality to parse FHEM values to function models (OnOff, Dimmer, ...).
mapping.set
This package provides the functionality to send FHEM commands to FHEM based on retrieved function object at 'PATCH /devices' endpoint.
